Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.87,0:00:21.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This scent... Could it be...?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.71,0:00:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Chopper, what's the matter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.30,0:00:30.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Chopper?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.76,0:00:35.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oops!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.22,0:00:39.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Chopper! Are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.64,0:00:42.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.48,0:00:43.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.02,0:00:47.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What on earth is going on...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.48,0:00:51.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Starting to run so sudden... ly...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.78,0:00:55.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew she'd be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.99,0:00:59.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Robin!\N--Robin-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.79,0:01:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't... return to you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.83,0:01:09.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're parting ways here... in this town...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.67,0:01:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I carry a darkness within me\Nthat you guys don't know about.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.92,0:01:18.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This darkness will destroy you someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.93,0:01:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As a matter of fact, I'm pinning this\Ncrime on you and planning to run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.39,0:01:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The situation will get worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.19,0:01:32.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin-chan! I don't get what you're saying!\NWhat happened to you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.53,0:01:35.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin! Let's go back together!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.45,0:01:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although I only spent a short\Ntime with you, after today...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.95,0:01:44.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'll never see you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.66,0:01:49.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for being nice to a person like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.96,0:01:51.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.63,0:01:59.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.14,0:02:02.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.76,0:02:05.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.98,0:02:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...accept this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.39,0:02:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.23,0:02:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop joking!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.15,0:02:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Robin-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.57,0:02:23.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.13,0:02:37.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I lost sight of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.72,0:02:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.84,0:02:44.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Chopper...\N--Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.26,0:02:50.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You go join Luffy and the others and tell\Nthem everything that just happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.77,0:02:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...without leaving a single word out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.27,0:02:57.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What're you gonna do?\N--We'll part ways here for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.15,0:03:01.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, don't worry. I won't do anything reckless.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.87,0:03:11.25,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right! Now let's move forward
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.25,0:03:14.79,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,with the sun always in our hearts
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.79,0:03:18.09,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,As power passes through our clasped hands
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.09,0:03:21.76,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,let's grab hold of our wishes
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.02,0:03:36.77,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Working together, let's ride the giant waves
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.77,0:03:44.07,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry toward the excitement--\Nthere's the starting signal
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.07,0:03:51.00,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Now's the time to set sail-- let's raise anchor
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.00,0:03:58.13,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut through the rainbow-colored wind\Nand head for a sea of adventure
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.13,0:04:01.55,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be a journey fraught with injury
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.55,0:04:05.51,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,but what you cherish most will be right there
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.51,0:04:09.52,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And if you get into a jam
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.52,0:04:12.60,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll always be there to protect you
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.60,0:04:16.69,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right! Now let's move forward
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.69,0:04:20.28,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,with the sun always in our hearts
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.28,0:04:23.28,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If a storm hits, let's put\Nour arms around each other
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.28,0:04:27.57,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and gaze at the light beyond
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.57,0:04:31.50,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If we gather up the pieces of our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.50,0:04:34.75,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,they'll make a map leading to tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.75,0:04:37.75,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,So let's grab hold of our wishes
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.75,0:04:43.51,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,under the same flag-- together, we're one
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.51,0:04:46.18,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,One Piece
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.18,0:05:02.15,B1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(2000,2000)}"Capture Robin!\NThe Determination of the Straw Hats"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.40,0:05:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hold it!\N--Hold it right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.11,0:05:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let them get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.12,0:05:13.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.58,0:05:14.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was going to happen eventually!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.96,0:05:17.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With this many people, it'd be\Nstrange if they didn't find us!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.71,0:05:20.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't get away from us anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.38,0:05:23.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.55,0:05:28.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.89,0:05:35.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.43,0:05:36.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where'd they go?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.52,0:05:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look in every nook and cranny!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.40,0:05:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about the alleys?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.86,0:05:42.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Couldn't they have climbed\Nup on some rooftop?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.19,0:05:44.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! They shook us off?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.69,0:05:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But they definitely ran in this direction!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.99,0:05:48.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we check over there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.78,0:05:50.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, we'll search inside the buildings!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.99,0:05:53.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, then! Let's split\Ninto two groups and search!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.58,0:05:55.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.00,0:05:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it okay now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.96,0:05:59.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.83,0:06:03.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you lose them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.38,0:06:07.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A bit longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.11,0:06:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.58,0:06:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.83,0:06:41.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come back some other time!\NI'm evacuating now. Stop pestering me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.29,0:06:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please... I've got money.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.30,0:06:50.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As much lumber, tar, and rope\Nas this amount will buy...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.26,0:06:53.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, some nails, latches, and tinplates...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.72,0:06:55.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm closing the shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.85,0:06:58.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... I'm sorry, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.81,0:07:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsk... Okay, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.61,0:07:08.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you can't buy that much\Nwith this little money.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.15,0:07:12.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Then, to make up for the rest,\NI'd like to exchange my tools.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.28,0:07:15.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, don't be ridiculous! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.12,0:07:19.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only sell. To think you're tryin' to barter...\NWhat are you, a bumpkin?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.88,0:07:30.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez... You win.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.97,0:07:42.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey! Are you okay carrying that\Nstuff when you're injured that badly?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.52,0:07:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Surely you have friends, right?! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.07,0:07:48.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See, what did I tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.21,0:08:08.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hold on a sec, lad!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.21,0:08:12.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm okay. This is nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.38,0:08:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hey!\N--What is it? Are you gonna...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.30,0:08:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.22,0:08:20.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here. Take these. You're hungry, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.98,0:08:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.19,0:08:28.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure... Be careful going back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.70,0:08:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful going back!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.13,0:08:50.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These're good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.09,0:08:53.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These're really good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.05,0:08:55.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a considerate pops he was.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.44,0:09:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The waves are getting quite high.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.36,0:09:20.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. It'll be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.46,0:09:32.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a ship... that flew in the sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.26,0:09:36.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.23,0:09:49.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.29,0:10:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Franky?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.01,0:10:21.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bro?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.97,0:10:24.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm getting ticked off!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.85,0:10:27.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's about time to\Ngo on another rampage!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.48,0:10:30.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bro! Wait for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.06,0:10:34.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the drink, Blueno!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.90,0:10:42.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to Franky\Nall of a sudden, Kokoro-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.95,0:10:53.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beats me... How should\NI know... how idiots think?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.43,0:11:07.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess things have finally calmed down.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.06,0:11:09.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Finally calmed down"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.18,0:11:12.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You had all those shipwrights chasing after you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.35,0:11:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why we ended up\Ngetting dragged into it, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.07,0:11:18.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said it was unavoidable, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.57,0:11:22.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, Chopper, I'm surprised\Nyou found out where we were.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.53,0:11:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Your scent.\N--Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.33,0:11:27.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? Come to think of it, where's Sanji?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.99,0:11:29.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.22,0:11:46.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did Robin really say that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.64,0:11:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.27,0:11:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We all... were prepared for it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.78,0:12:03.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though it was for a\Nshort time, we let Robin,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.41,0:12:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who showed up as an enemy, come on board.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.91,0:12:10.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be embarrassing if we ran\Naway because we got scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.54,0:12:15.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it about time for us to settle this matter...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.50,0:12:20.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...as to whether that woman is... foe or friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.65,0:12:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The situation will get worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.40,0:12:43.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After today... I'll never see you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.37,0:12:51.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're sure that Robin said that, Chopper?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.33,0:12:53.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.92,0:12:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She said she wouldn't see us after today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.42,0:13:01.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It also sounds like she's\Ndeclaring that she'll do something
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.25,0:13:03.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that could worsen the situation\Nbefore the day is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.97,0:13:10.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at how big a fuss
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.26,0:13:13.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the attempted assassination of\Nthe mayor caused in this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.48,0:13:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's possible to make the situation worse,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.56,0:13:18.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there's only one thing she can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.86,0:13:22.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This time for sure... Assassinate the mayor...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.86,0:13:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's natural to think that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.82,0:13:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we know that she's pinning\Nher crime on us on purpose,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.75,0:13:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so it's possible that this could be a trap\Nto lure us out to the scene of the crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.00,0:13:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trap...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.50,0:13:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we're at the spot of the\Nassassination carried out tonight,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.00,0:13:45.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the crime will easily be pinned on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.59,0:13:50.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! You already sound\Nlike Robin is really our foe!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.80,0:13:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm talking about the possibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.27,0:13:55.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that I've decided on either.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.35,0:14:00.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I already decide either to believe her or not,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.19,0:14:02.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if the truth turns out to\Nbe the opposite of that...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.82,0:14:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...it'll slow down my reaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.32,0:14:14.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If something is to happen,\Nit'll be tonight. Are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.45,0:14:16.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.76,0:14:31.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind going... but there's a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.01,0:14:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji-kun saw Robin walking\Nwith someone, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.10,0:14:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Iceberg-san said the same thing.\NShe was with someone with a mask on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.27,0:14:43.57,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,"Mr. Iceberg Falls Victim to Assassin"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.23,0:14:45.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it wasn't any of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.11,0:14:47.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He must be the reason why\NRobin suddenly changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.32,0:14:52.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't he making Robin do bad things?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.28,0:14:54.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That would be fortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.62,0:14:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If this guy is Robin's real friend,\Nthen that would be misfortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.79,0:15:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But "someone with a mask on"\Ncan't be a clue. That's the problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.25,0:15:06.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's our goal?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.13,0:15:08.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll capture Robin.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.56,0:15:19.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise, we won't know anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.52,0:15:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,True. Thinking about it is a waste of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.77,0:15:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, come to think of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.90,0:15:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the World Government has been trying\Nto capture that woman for twenty years,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.65,0:15:31.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and yet, it still hasn't happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.61,0:15:36.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if we wanna know the truth,\Nthat's the only way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.54,0:15:40.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'll do my best, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.08,0:15:42.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, let's go...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.12,0:15:44.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to Galley-La Company!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.42,0:15:53.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! The night is coming at last.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.59,0:15:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Paulie-san! This is it! The backstreets\Nwill become dangerous soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.93,0:16:01.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Let's go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.39,0:16:02.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna head to the main office.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.56,0:16:04.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.19,0:16:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, guys! We're going back!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.65,0:16:12.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat! Show yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.32,0:16:14.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where're you hiding?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.82,0:16:19.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat! That bastard...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.24,0:16:22.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought the guy had at least a bit of mettle.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.33,0:16:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he doesn't even show himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.79,0:16:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Bro, the entire island holds\Na grudge against them right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.63,0:16:33.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's right. They must be\Nrunning from place to place.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.34,0:16:37.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, what's the matter?\NWhat're you guys doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.68,0:16:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're vulnerable to strong winds from the front.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.06,0:16:47.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, Bro, the way you're\Nraging today is different from usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.19,0:16:50.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Letting stuff build up inside you isn't like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.78,0:16:53.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! I'm like that this week!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.90,0:16:56.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Bro!\N--Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.49,0:16:59.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Bro! Bro!\N--That's Zambai and the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.95,0:17:04.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bro! Did you beat up those bastards?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.37,0:17:05.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.75,0:17:08.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was some crazy\Ninterference. They got away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.59,0:17:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.71,0:17:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They got away from you when you were angry?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.26,0:17:14.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What strong luck they have!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.92,0:17:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... Since that weak long-nosed guy\Nwas fixing their ship all by himself,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.26,0:17:24.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just assumed that you beat up the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.93,0:17:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You found one of them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.15,0:17:29.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y... Yes, on their ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.28,0:17:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you've found one of them, that makes it easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.86,0:17:41.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can use him to drag them all out!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.12,0:17:44.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-Bro is showing his bad guy face.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.91,0:17:50.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, you guys! Starting now,\Nmarch throughout the town...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.13,0:17:53.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...shouting, "We've got Long-nose!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.09,0:17:55.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't want him to sink in the sea,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.09,0:17:57.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,come to the warehouse under the bridge!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.63,0:18:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Franky sends his regards!"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.47,0:18:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To make it true, I'm gonna\Ngo kidnap Long-nose.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.39,0:18:12.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Bro! Leave it to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.21,0:18:36.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're big, but your baggage is big, too, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.13,0:18:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my special bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.38,0:18:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aqua Laguna! Aqua Laguna!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.59,0:18:45.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aqua Laguna is coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.64,0:18:48.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're Aqua Laguna!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.18,0:18:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.35,0:18:52.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what's going on with those culprits?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.56,0:18:55.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that they haven't been caught after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.15,0:18:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How disturbing. Ahh, what a pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.36,0:19:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's said that they might attack again\Ntonight in the confusion of the storm.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.58,0:19:06.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aqua Laguna is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.33,0:19:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it'll be crazy tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.83,0:19:13.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that all the craftsmen\Nwill be guarding the main office.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.04,0:19:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! That's pretty serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.55,0:19:19.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How many are there in the Straw Hat Pirates?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.17,0:19:24.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some people said 50. Others said 100.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.01,0:19:26.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The captain's got a 100 million\Nbounty on his head, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.85,0:19:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some said that 3,000 of his men\Nwould advance from the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.10,0:19:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds totally dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.36,0:19:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Galley-La Company! Form a line,\Nand don't leave any openings!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.62,0:19:45.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.24,0:19:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't allow even a single rat inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.87,0:19:50.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.97,0:20:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.77,0:20:15.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, coo coo! Be quiet, Tilestone!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.06,0:20:18.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was told that they weren't on the sea train.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.02,0:20:22.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then they're still somewhere\Non this island, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.03,0:20:25.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But they're fools if they really\Nappear with all these guards around.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.41,0:20:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that an idiot plunged in here\Nin the middle of the day today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.62,0:20:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't think using your common sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.42,0:20:36.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.83,0:20:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They don't have to go this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.63,0:20:42.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're doing it voluntarily.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.55,0:20:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're treating me like a king.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.38,0:20:49.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, why did you put up Nico\NRobin's wanted poster in your room?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.85,0:20:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you curious?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.23,0:20:54.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A little.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.27,0:21:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's better if you don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.57,0:21:06.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She is... a devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.81,0:21:36.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tons of people are guarding the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.31,0:21:38.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a little far.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.31,0:21:40.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can just stretch your arm\Nand go flying there, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.48,0:21:42.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But after the commotion starts, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.28,0:21:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. If we cause a commotion before\Nthey do, they'll just take advantage of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.20,0:21:50.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.03,0:21:52.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't miss even the slightest movement!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.70,0:21:56.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.69,0:22:23.11,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,A piece of a dream that we started grasping
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.11,0:22:26.65,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Chasing after something constant
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.65,0:22:32.24,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We send our aspirations sailing into the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.24,0:22:34.54,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Even when we're exhausted
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.54,0:22:37.71,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We have a compass that can\Nsearch for something constant
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.71,0:22:43.13,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, do you think we can keep it forever?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.13,0:22:46.05,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,At the end of the dream\Nthat we will reach someday
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.05,0:22:49.01,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We want to be adults as we\Nare now as much as possible
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.01,0:22:51.80,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We pray to this endless sky that we look up at
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.80,0:22:54.89,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Eternally... Eternally...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.89,0:22:57.68,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Wild fantasies from our childhood
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.68,0:23:00.52,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We trace unforgettable memories
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.52,0:23:06.19,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And try to keep the embers\Nburning that still consume us
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.19,0:23:09.03,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,To this familiar sunny sky
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.03,0:23:11.82,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Together we entrust our feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.82,0:23:14.41,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We go beyond the changing time
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.41,0:23:19.04,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Eternally... Eternally...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.13,0:23:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that explosion?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.75,0:23:28.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So they've finally started taking action.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.42,0:23:31.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The craftsmen are being\Nattacked by weird people!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.18,0:23:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin is definitely in that commotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.30,0:23:36.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen. Think that we'll never be able to\Nsee Robin again if we miss this chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.93,0:23:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know. We'll definitely\Ncapture her. Just wait, Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.39,0:23:43.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.02,0:23:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Cannon Fire Is the Signal!\NCP9 Goes into Action"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.52,0:23:48.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
